source.name: NOLA Census 1990
source.description: 1990 City of New Orleans/Orleans Parish Census data.  ESRI shapefile format, GIS software required for viewing geometry (http://www.esri.com/software/arcgis/arcreader/).  Tabular data (DBF), included as part of the shapefile, are viewable in Excel.
